			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hiya all...<BR>
<BR>
About the rod in Lake Rathe:  I got a wolf form and enduring breath from a high lvl druid friend.  AND an invis.  See the problem is that some of the deepwater gobbies see thru invis, some don't... if you con from a distance you'll see what I mean.  They also neglected to mention that Deep is in there too!!!  She conned red to my 54th lvl friend.  BUT was indifferent; in a previous attempt I almost smacked right into her, but I only had regular invis on... she conned indifferent.  SO, it seems that Deep does NOT see thru regular invis, but there is a chance that one or more of the DW gobbies DO, therefore get a wolf form AND an invis.  The gobs don't aggro wolf form.<BR>
<BR>
Hope this helps.<BR>
