				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				If find this to be an excellent quest for a wizard to do. Perfect at level 20! <BR>
I had no trouble with the rods. Didn't see any sharks around in Erud's Xing. <BR>
For lake Rathe Rod get a friendly druid to help you and cast Enduring breath and Wolf form onto you. Wolf form is the key here because you won't be KOS to goblins in Wolf form. <BR>
I only died once and that was in Qeynos Undergrounds.. <BR>
(Ran into a spectre.. Doh!)<BR>
In Lower Guk I shouted for a guide for 30 minutes. Make sure you go there at peak times during the weekend. The place is full of people. <BR>
<BR>
Good luck in your quest for the wheel<BR>
*proudly shows his new staff to everyone*
